{"name":"Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook without manual work","nodes":[{"parameters":{"formTitle":"Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook without manua","formFields":{"values":[{"fieldLabel":"Email","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Company","requiredField":false},{"fieldLabel":"Score","requiredField":false}]},"options":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"8674cedd-6a52-48c6-8881-ae74ce7417aa","name":"New Lead Form Submission","webhookId":"71a617a1-d716-45b3-ab35-d39f3da82a2a"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"df77168e-af1b-4302-b194-edbf78f15297","leftValue":"={{ $json.leadId || $json.email }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.filter","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[54,400],"id":"4a096522-b9c9-4569-8782-1090fcd19a86","name":"Keep Valid Leads"},{"parameters":{"compare":"selectedFields","fieldsToCompare":"leadId","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.removeDuplicates","typeVersion":2,"position":[378,400],"id":"22e07ec9-553b-4bea-9051-80a0fc519305","name":"Remove Duplicate Leads"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"query","value":"={{ $json.email }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[702,400],"id":"a544aea1-79f0-4df9-975b-06383dbb20e9","name":"Enrich — Primary Provider","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"03393e0d-68b0-4cb6-9df7-6b4f21b210a8","leftValue":"={{ $json.company || $json.name }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[1026,400],"id":"e93f5a0c-cd45-4c1f-a655-4ba517595cb9","name":"Primary Hit?"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://fallback-enrich.example.com/v1/person","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"email","value":"={{ $json.email }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[1350,880],"id":"d7408f4c-690b-4975-b8d0-71796834229c","name":"Enrich — Fallback Provider","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[1998,400],"id":"adb63f49-b605-4f31-a86d-7aca10c0766a","name":"Merge Enrichment Paths"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Score each lead 0-100 from simple heuristics\nreturn $input.all().map(item => {\n  const j = item.json;\n  let score = 50;\n  if (j.email) score += 20;\n  if (j.company) score += 15;\n  if ((j.source || '') === 'referral') score += 15;\n  return { json: { ...j, score: Math.min(100, score) } };\n});"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[2970,400],"id":"5f77b243-64a1-4352-9750-de9b82314aac","name":"Score Enriched Records"},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[3294,400],"id":"200ee6d6-6d31-4d34-a069-fa0ac511916d","name":"Upsert into HubSpot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"c60d0a59-3401-4cd4-bdd4-22474d028f09","leftValue":"={{ $json.score >= 80 }}","rightValue":true,"operator":{"type":"boolean","operation":"true"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[3618,400],"id":"a1350d99-23f3-42a2-ac1b-68cacf539e66","name":"Hot Lead?"},{"parameters":{"subject":"=🔥 Hot {{ $json.company || $json.email }} (score {{ $json.score }}) — reach out ","bodyContent":"=🔥 Hot {{ $json.company || $json.email }} (score {{ $json.score }}) — reach out now","toRecipients":"={{ $json.email || 'ops@company.com' }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[3942,160],"id":"e8768bb5-e98d-42fa-8208-ff8461ce39c6","name":"Ping Owner Immediately","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"completedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[4266,400],"id":"51bd88f5-92ba-42f9-99f2-40843bfd5537","name":"Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"dataToSave":{"values":[{"key":"runId","value":"={{ $execution.id }}"},{"key":"itemCount","value":"={{ $items().length }}"}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.executionData","typeVersion":1,"position":[4590,400],"id":"8740ee94-451b-4c0e-b020-acdc75fad491","name":"Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"query","value":"={{ $json.email }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[4914,400],"id":"e1fb8c8b-0aaf-41cc-905c-de10ffcd249c","name":"Enrich with Reference Data","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"f365d9f2-9221-48f3-9e49-81ff515f3c4e","name":"enrichedAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"3fe2e7c7-9c44-42c2-9643-b06604979b6f","name":"enrichmentSource","value":"reference-api","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5238,400],"id":"146b426c-a466-48a7-979f-1a267c8bd656","name":"Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Build a stable idempotency key per lead (djb2 hash, no deps)\nfunction hash(s) {\n  let h = 5381;\n  for (let i = 0; i < s.length; i++) h = ((h << 5) + h + s.charCodeAt(i)) >>> 0;\n  return h.toString(16);\n}\nreturn $input.all().map(item => {\n  const j = item.json;\n  return { json: { ...j, idempotencyKey: hash([j.leadId, j.email].join('|')) } };\n});"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[5562,400],"id":"a2afdda5-598f-40e2-9e14-814029f3255b","name":"Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"operation":"removeItemsSeenInPreviousExecutions","logic":"removeItemsWithAlreadySeenKeyValues","dedupeValue":"={{ $json.idempotencyKey }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.removeDuplicates","typeVersion":2,"position":[5886,400],"id":"3f6a482b-3c7e-4147-bf6d-8ea5db4064c5","name":"Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"d3b7bc00-97d4-4756-8964-c6e88d0a778b","name":"runAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"d4f484ab-e23f-4ba1-93f6-e7b80b10c1f2","name":"itemCount","value":"={{ $input.all().length }}","type":"number"},{"id":"0bcffe2f-7b9f-4f90-a4d6-27d720377890","name":"status","value":"completed","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[6210,400],"id":"1cb916a6-a1f4-4a91-a1ec-7e54d75f7b04","name":"Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[6534,400],"id":"93e8996a-7553-4d6b-93f6-deca88917e58","name":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"subject":"=✅ Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook without manual work — run comp","bodyContent":"=✅ Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook without manual work — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","toRecipients":"={{ $json.email || 'ops@company.com' }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[6858,400],"id":"c683fe5b-b0ae-4e24-a5f0-7b046690147d","name":"Send Summary to Outlook","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"5a2db978-74cb-401a-9d77-5313bfe3fa24","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"8662f5a8-83f5-40bf-b468-a53de90b5324","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"3869364b-bf24-4278-a389-f333f46f9355","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[6210,1420],"id":"3a0affed-13a1-4d28-b111-951e294a0466","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"subject":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage ","bodyContent":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","toRecipients":"={{ $json.email || 'ops@company.com' }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[6534,1420],"id":"38f00b7d-2853-4ff8-9ec2-9824e2180a1d","name":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[6858,1420],"id":"f251da31-4f94-4ec7-9712-6dba72f73d31","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### New Lead Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (Email, Company, Score). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Keep Valid Leads","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"00ee1430-6cb8-f179-d7b8-9a63454780e3","name":"Note: New Lead Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Keep Valid Leads\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Remove Duplicate Leads","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"885acde0-a61c-db9d-2eda-5e943ffffa9f","name":"Note: Keep Valid Leads"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Remove Duplicate Leads\n\nDrops duplicates within this run (compared on `leadId`).\n\nNext: Enrich — Primary Provider","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"c0316be6-fc8b-0375-9927-ec9ed459bc29","name":"Note: Remove Duplicate Leads"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich — Primary Provider\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Primary Hit? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"4dc7b6ea-5e66-8780-5edc-de348c75f8c3","name":"Note: Enrich — Primary Provider"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Primary Hit?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.company || $json.name }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Enrichment Paths · ②→ Enrich — Fallback Provider","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"c11ddf9e-6d17-9671-a734-9b38192534cd","name":"Note: Primary Hit?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich — Fallback Provider\n\nGET https://fallback-enrich.example.com/v1/person — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Enrichment Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1000],"id":"ad0c8396-e7a7-488c-0614-e6f03c17367e","name":"Note: Enrich — Fallback Provider"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Enrichment Paths\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Score Enriched Records","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"83eeffbb-0502-dcc6-553f-66b5a9290974","name":"Note: Merge Enrichment Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Score Enriched Records\n\nCustom JavaScript: Score each lead 0-100 from simple heuristics\n\nNext: Upsert into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"304a7eb2-9d02-492b-e5aa-90a07fc7d68d","name":"Note: Score Enriched Records"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert into HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hot Lead? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"a646e81d-8e9e-bdb4-7b90-a89801253cbd","name":"Note: Upsert into HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hot Lead?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.score >= 80 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Ping Owner Immediately · ②→ Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"5c459e3c-dacf-2ce4-d47c-d2df8c11dff5","name":"Note: Hot Lead?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Ping Owner Immediately\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,280],"id":"40c555c6-931b-5cb9-3059-0e2a93c0d025","name":"Note: Ping Owner Immediately"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"b5c1b31d-a93b-1128-6f83-013b4f4e101e","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"4e7135cc-d56f-3135-8169-8b71b55c198c","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"55aaf493-6f70-02cb-ccb1-a618c580bad5","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"7fea49bb-5a3f-c63e-d7fe-09ec122c2b2e","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per lead (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"37a70d3c-afcd-551d-a765-21d8375c3df8","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"238980b7-c061-45d6-8370-15b30b7d980d","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"4d07981e-3c6d-8a4e-e794-a91d722964e1","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Outlook · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"1118fed6-5f58-34a5-0740-e3e6342f53e6","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"914d9279-684a-2dd3-76be-6ae1b7b7583a","name":"Note: Send Summary to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Outlook","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,1540],"id":"19ee5525-f65b-d133-1fc4-6afdc5269ac5","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,1540],"id":"9377a609-c250-27af-929a-57ea37c0835d","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,1540],"id":"2dcd8daa-c517-665b-4eb6-0f9b3e6de367","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Lead Capture & Routing · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nQualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook without manual work. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual capture forms is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Keep Valid Leads → Remove Duplicate Leads → Enrich — Primary Provider → Primary Hit? → Merge Enrichment Paths → Score Enriched Records → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to lead capture & routing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating capture forms in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Improves response time\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; HubSpot private-app token; Microsoft OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"12728b43-a3e2-f001-47bc-c8ccc44890ee","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"28e374ca-604b-28cf-5456-124e18541d68","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"c2f44f7d-1096-acea-0f14-7d8360a8e9b0","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your capture forms process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"4b0d9344-6b7d-1dd4-b1bf-a2ee4748f750","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Lead Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Keep Valid Leads","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Keep Valid Leads":{"main":[[{"node":"Remove Duplicate Leads","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Remove Duplicate Leads":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich — Primary Provider","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich — Primary Provider":{"main":[[{"node":"Primary Hit?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Primary Hit?":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Enrichment Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Enrich — Fallback Provider","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich — Fallback Provider":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Enrichment Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Enrichment Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Score Enriched Records","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Score Enriched Records":{"main":[[{"node":"Upsert into HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upsert into HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Hot Lead?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hot Lead?":{"main":[[{"node":"Ping Owner Immediately","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Outlook":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Ping Owner Immediately":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Outlook":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"93d8ed35-3f93-4781-b7db-e7f1f1cfb7e9","id":"FDX04338"}